Effect.PerformanceRealization: %r% dredged up some of %ip% embarrassing past

%i% gained %rp% respect with that embarrassing joke

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Oh, hey, %r%! Wanna hear a joke?
What do you call a cow that's just given birth to a calf?

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: %random(Die in a fire,I hate you,You die now,Burning... rage...)%.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Oh, hey, %r%! Wanna hear a joke?

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Sure, why not?

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Where do baby cows eat?
The calf-eteria!

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: ...ok, that IS kind of cute.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Oh, hey, %r%! You should come over some time and check out my %toc1% collection!

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: You have GOT to be kidding me.
Get lost before your lameness infects us all.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: %greeting%, %r%. Hey, can I show you something?

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Oh god, is this going to be like that time when %toc1%?

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Why'd you have to bring that up?
%r%! I just heard a really terrible joke. You're going to think I'm superlame for even repeating it.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: What! I am not, %sweetie%. Try me.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Why was the calf afraid?

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: I don't know, %sweetie%... why?

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: He was a cow-herd.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Oh, you're so precious. Where do you come up with these? You're the coolest.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: %r%! I just heard this awful calf joke. You're going to love it.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Oh god, wait...

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: What did the calf say to the silo?
Is my fodder in there?

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: %i%, you have real guts to repeat that joke in public. I'm... I'm proud to %if(0,be your friend)else(know you)%.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: %r%! Hi! Hey wow, you're looking absolutely gorgeous today!
Uh, I mean... good. Or okay. Just... yeah. Not that I'm... I mean, I'm not...
Sorry, that was totally inappropriate. I'm such an idiot. I'm a total %pejorative% actually. You shouldn't even be talking to me.
I mean, how could a beautiful %gender(r,man,woman)% like you ever date a terrible person like me? Uh, I mean, not that anyone said anything about, uh....
Hey, %buddy%... I've been working on some new moves. Here, check this out.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: %i%... that's pathetic. I can't believe you would do something like that in public.
Now watch and learn.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Oh hey %buddy%... can you help me figure out how to delete all of these embarrassing pictures of me off my phone?

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Oh yeah sure. You just tap select all and then swipe up with three fingers and then diagonal down to the left with four fingers, then vertical shake to confirm.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Like this?

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Yeah. Wait, did you double-tap select all?

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Uh, maybe... why?

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: I think that selects everyone in your address book. You just sent those photos to everyone in school. Also apparently the college admissions board.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Hi %r%! Hey, check out what I've got in my hand.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Ughh. what the hell is that?

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: It's a %toc1%!

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Oh, gross! WTF is wrong with you? Who just carries around a %toc1% all the time?

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Hey %r%. Do you want to know something about me?

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: %random(Uh... sure?,Well... maybe?,Do I have a choice?,Probably not.,Uh... why not.)%

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: When I was little, %random(I liked to drink water out of puddles,I used to watch that Vanilla Ice movie over and over again,I shoved a bagel up my nose,I liked to put ketchup on my breakfast cereal,I ate a whole family of snails,I had fleas once and I named them and made them my friends,I used to have a rat tail haircut)%.

Whoa- I hope nobody %random(saw me trip and spill my drink all over,saw me almost faceplant on those stairs,heard my stomach make that weird noise,saw me trying to push that 'pull' door for like five minutes,saw that piece of toilet paper stuck to my shoe,heard me singing along to that country song,saw that video I posted defending Justin Beiber)% earlier.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Are you kidding? I think everyone saw it. It's probably all over the internet by now.
Oh yeah, it totally is.
Uh, %i%, are you okay? You've been staring at the wall for like five minutes.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: ...what? Sorry, did you say something to me just now?

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Pull yourself together, %gender(i,man,girl)%.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: %r%, I'd like you to hear something. %random(It's a jazzy rendition of the national anthem I've been working on,It's some free verse poetry about pimples I wrote last week,A love letter I wrote to my future life partner,It's a story about unicorns I wrote in fourth grade and just found in my grandma's attic,It's an entry from my diary about the journey of self-discovery my therapist and I have gone through over the past two years,It's the theme from M.A.S.H. arranged for solo yodeler,It's a performance involving spoken word and interpretive dance that represents my feelings towards you)%.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Uhhhh, that's okay, %i%. %random(I really have other things to,I really should be going,I'm kinda busy,I'd rather not,I don't think that)%...

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Part One: Ekphrasis...

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Oh god...

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Hey, %r%, want to hear a bad joke? %random(What do you need if you have bird flu? ...TWEETMENT!,Where do people from Florida wash their clothes? ...Fort LAUNDERdale!,What kind of eggs does an evil chicken lay? ...deviled eggs.,Did you hear about the fire at the circus? It was in TENTS.,What do you call a rifle with three barrels? ...A TRIFLE.,What do prisoners use to call each other? ...CELL phones.,How did the pig get to the hospital? ...In a HAMbulance.,Why is a dog like a phone? ...They both have COLLAR ID!,What does a lawyer wear to work? ...a LAW SUIT!,Did you hear the paint store got robbed? ...It was a VIOLET crime!)%

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: OMGZ %i%, that's hilARious!
I'm totally texting that to my friends.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Hey %r%, want to hear an embarrassing story about me?

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Well, I can't imagine anything you could say that could make me think you were any less cool. Shoot.
OK, you were wrong, that's hilarious.
